##Video editing
* Juliette & Heerko's video remixing tool
* OBS (Open Broadcaster Software)

## (Collaborative) Coding 
* Glitch: https://glitch.com 

## Vector drawing
* Processing (requires programming)
* Inkscape (similar to Illustrator)

## 3D design
* Blender
* Antimony

## Publishing tools
* Sarah Garcin's PJ machine
* MKdocs
* RISO printer


